        <Summary>A Chat Application for LANs</Summary>
        <Description>TriX - serverless chat for small home or office LANs running Linux. TriX chat based on the VyQChat. The project is released 
under terms of GNU GPLv2 license. As compared to VyQChat in TriX such new features appears as: files transfer, users avatars, logs, links navigation, 
broadcast and multicast type of connection, search by IP address and many other, not listed here things. TriX is compatible with 2.0 protocol version 
of the Vypress Chat (TM) developed by VyPRESS Research, but there are some protocol differences in TriX (needs to support avatars).</Description>
